# Echo — read a character, display it with decreasing fidelity
#
# Demonstrates: listen, measure, inject, filter
# Input a character, then watch it decay as noise accumulates.

channel input
channel display

// Read one character
listen input

// Copy to display channel for manipulation
copy input -> display

// Output 1: clean
measure display

// Output 2: slightly noisy
inject display * 3
measure display

// Output 3: filtered back
filter display * 3
measure display

emit "\n"
